# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TxReceipts — optional server-side API keys (read by the backend in src/app/api/*).
#
# Everything works KEYLESS out of the box:
#   • EVM (Ethereum, Base, Polygon, Sepolia) → Blockscout public tier
#   • Bitcoin → mempool.space (with blockstream.info fallback)
#   • Prices → CoinGecko
#
# These keys are OPTIONAL and only raise rate limits / unlock Solana. They are
# read server-side ONLY (no NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefix) so they never reach the browser.
# Copy this file to ".env.local" and fill in what you need.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Etherscan V2 multichain key — ONE key covers Ethereum, Base, Polygon & Sepolia.
# Without it, EVM scans use the keyless Blockscout tier.
# Get one free at https://etherscan.io/myapikey
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=

# Helius key — REQUIRED to scan Solana addresses (there is no keyless option).
# Get one free at https://dev.helius.xyz
HELIUS_API_KEY=
